              dnl But don't add it
              dnl   1. if it's the standard /usr/include,
              dnl   2. if it's /usr/local/include and we are using GCC on Linux,
              dnl   3. if it's already present in $CPPFLAGS or the already
              dnl      constructed $INCNAME,
